'''人类蛋白质组计划'''（{{lang|en|Human proteome project}}，缩写：HPP）<ref>Legrain, P. et al. The human proteome project: Current state and future direction. Mol Cell Proteomics. 10:M111.009993 (2011).</ref>是由[[人类蛋白质组组织|人类蛋白质组组织]]（HUPO）<ref>HUPO (Human Proteome Organization) 1st World Congress. Mol Cell Proteomics. 9:651-752 (2002).</ref>协调的合作计划，目标是通过[[实验|实验]]观察所有从[[人类基因组|人类基因组]][[翻譯_(生物學)|翻译]]序列产生的[[蛋白质|蛋白质]]。

== 历史 == 
人类蛋白质组组织已成为许多长期运行的蛋白质组学研究项目的协调机构，这些研究项目与临床兴趣的特定人体组织有关，如[[血浆|血浆]]<ref>Omenn, G.S. et al. Overview of the HUPO Plasma Proteome Project. ''Proteomics''. 5, 3226-45 (2005).</ref>，[[肝|肝]]<ref>He, F. Human liver proteome project: plan, progress, and perspectives. Mol Cell Proteomics. 4, 1841-8 (2005).</ref>，[[脑|脑]]<ref>Hamacher, M. et al. HUPO Brain Proteome Project: toward a code of conduct. Mol Cell Proteomics. 7, 457 (2008).</ref>，和[[尿|尿]]<ref>Yamamoto, T., Langham, R.G., Ronco, P., Knepper, M.A. & Thongboonkerd, V. Towards standard protocols and guidelines for urine proteomics. ''Proteomics''. 8, 2156-9 (2008).</ref>。它还负责与蛋白质大规模研究相关的具体技术<ref>Uhlen, M. & Ponten, F. Antibody-based proteomics for human tissue profiling. Mol Cell Proteomics. 4, 384-93 (2005).</ref>和标准<ref>Orchard, S. et al. Current status of proteomic standards development. Expert Rev Proteomics. 1, 179-83 (2005).</ref>。

在科学文献中，将平行于[[人类基因组计划|人类基因组计划]]的一个更大项目的结构和目标被辩论<ref>Archakov A, et al. The Moscow HUPO Human Proteome Project workshop.
Mol Cell Proteomics. 8:2199-200 (2009).</ref><ref>Baker MS. Building the 'practical' human proteome project - the next big thing in basic and clinical proteomics. Curr Opin Mol Ther. 2009 11:600-2 (2009).</ref><ref>Editorial, The call of the human proteome. Nat Methods. 7:661 (2010).</ref><ref>Rabilloud T., et al. Is a gene-centric human proteome project the best way for proteomics to serve biology? ''Proteomics''. 10:3067-72 (2010).</ref><ref>Editorial. A Gene-centric Human Proteome Project. Mol Cell Proteomics. 9:427-429 (2010).</ref>。经过2009年、2010年和2011年世界大会和一系列会议，人类蛋白质组组织将人类蛋白质组计划分为两个子项目C-HPP和B/D-HPP进行<ref>Paik, Y-K., et al. A Chromosome-Centric Human Proteome Project to Characterize the Sets of Proteins Encoded in the Genome. Nature Biotech.30: 221–3(2012).</ref>。其中C-HPP将分成25工作组，每个[[人类染色体|人类染色体]]1个工作组。而B/D-HPP将按照蛋白质的生物学和疾病相关性进行分组<ref>Aebersold R., et al. The Biology/Disease-driven Human Proteome Project (B/D-HPP): Enabling Protein Research for the Life Sciences Community. ''J. Proteome Res''. 12:23–27 (2013).</ref>。

